// Philosophy Section - Kind not nice
---

<section class="bg-brand-dark py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-12 text-center">
        Kind, not nice.
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-brand-muted">
        <p>
          Most coaches tell you what you want to hear.
        </p>

        <p>
          I tell you what you need to hear.
        </p>

        <p>
          When you skip and say "work was crazy," I'm going to say: <span class="text-brand-text">"Work's been crazy for three years. That's not a reason anymore, that's your life. So what's the actual plan?"</span>
        </p>

        <p>
          Not to make you feel bad. To make the excuse sound as ridiculous out loud as it should sound in your head.
        </p>

        <p class="text-brand-text font-semibold">
          That's the job.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
